### Update Driver Verification Status
PATCH https://hello-truck-server.fly.dev/admin/drivers/DRIVER_ID/verification
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

{
  "status": "VERIFIED",
  "licenseExpiry": "2026-12-31",
  "fcExpiry": "2026-12-31",
  "insuranceExpiry": "2026-12-31"
}

### Update Driver Verification Status (Local)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/admin/drivers/DRIVER_ID/verification
Content-Type: application/json
